INSERT [dbo].[AssociatedDocumentationCategoryPage] ([Id], [Content], [CategoryField], [Title]) VALUES (1008, N'<p>Rokono Control follows modern day best practices of version control using fully integrated git module, the whole idea behind our tool is to connect teams and contributors together in order to create the perfect working environment.  We have developed several tools that are meant to be used alongside the platform in order to increase productivity, maintenance and management. Planning and contributing is not enough, in order to have good and clean project management your team leads need to know the flow of information within their field of reach. We acknowledge that, thus we want to help you out by   giving you the tools to maintain your project. When the managers create the internal structure of the project, developers/contributors have the option to use either our command line tool or the desktop application in order to push changes to the project repository and associated their commits with the internal task ids, allowing managers to associate changes with actual work items thus visualizing everything.</p><p><br></p><p>The desktop application:</p><ul><li>easy to use file browser</li><li>Commit History</li><li>Staging</li><li>Blaming</li><li>Code comparison</li><li>Post a comment </li><li>Drag and drop multiple work items for a single commit</li><li>Rollback changes</li></ul><p>CLI Tool: </p><ul><li>easy to use file browser</li><li>Commit History</li><li>Staging</li><li>Blaming</li><li>Code comparison</li><li>Post a comment</li><li>Drag and drop multiple work items for a single commit</li><li>Rollback changes</li></ul><p><br></p><p>	</p>', 7, N'Source Control')
GO
INSERT [dbo].[AssociatedDocumentationCategoryPage] ([Id], [Content], [CategoryField], [Title]) VALUES (1009, N'<h1>Project Management</h1><p><br></p><p>We have built our tool around the agile project management methodologies, we took a deep study and feedback from several renowned project managers with over 20 years of experience in the field in order to bring the best practices in the agile field to our product. From the advanced planning boards, to the discussion boards for each work item, to personalized experience for each of the different members of your team we have built the perfect working environment. Build work item relations, attach diagrams, track teams, assign iterations and break up complicated tasks. You can do it all and much more, track all of your working using the powerful widget building system that allows team members to personalize a board, create their own widgets or use some of the ones that come with the platform by default.</p>', 7, N'Agile ')
